ðŸ’» Installation Instructions
Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/ImageToolbox.git
Install dependencies using your preferred package manager (e.g., Gradle).
Build the project:
bash ./gradlew build
Run the application:
bash ./gradlew run
